Pioneer Corp. Africa to Issue 800 Million Shares After Unifreight Purchase

-- B y   G o d f r e y   M a r a w a n y i k a
-- 
2011-07-19T10:03:06Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-19/pioneer-corp-africa-to-issue-800-million-shares-after-unifreight-purchase.html
Pioneer Corp. (6773)  Africa Ltd., a
transport company, plans to issue 800 million shares after
completing the acquisition of Unifreight Zimbabwe Ltd., the
company said.  Pioneer also plans to consolidate shares at a ratio of 10
to 1, the Harare-based company said in a circular to
shareholders today. The share issue will bring total authorized
shares to 1.4 billion, it said.    To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Gordon Bell at 
 gbell16@bloomberg.net  